Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柴崎高中數學老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在第二層
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,24歲 單身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也算是個正經的成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天午休的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A班的佐竹在走廊上把妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會選地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說他把的誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A班的日下部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說那傢伙是不是有點得意忘形啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我承認她可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是出去玩一下有什麼不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還以為自己是偶像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是偶像的話 應該會更注意態度的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再響亮一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合格 可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來沒什麼煩惱真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上給我小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺空氣好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日下部？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.22,0:22:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 亞人醬有話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.19,0:23:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高橋鐵男想要保護
